<TEXT>
<P>
   ALL BUDGETED STORIES HAVE MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   Recapping:
</P>
<P>
   The following were eliminated from tonight's NYTNS budgets:
</P>
<P>
   BRADLEY-SUPPORTERS (Washington)
</P>
<P>
   KY-POLICE-SHOOTING (Louisville, Ky.)
</P>
<P>
   FLA-AUTO-PILEUP (Wellborn, Fla.)
</P>
<P>
