<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX WASHINGTON BUREAU CORRECTION
 &HT;    By RICK CHRISTIE 
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ In the story, LEBANON-AMNESIA-$ADV05, that moved
Thurs., March 2, for publication Sun., March 5, the Cox News
Service gave the incorrect first name for the missing husband of
Wadad Helwani, leader of a Lebanese families group.
</P>
<P>
   The correct name of her husand is as follows: Adnan Helwani.
</P>
<P>
   The Cox News Service regrets the error.
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
</P>
