   &UR; SHAMELESS KOHL RETURNS, WAVING BUNDLES OF MONEY &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   BERLIN _ The great fund-raiser is back. Ex-Chancellor Helmut
Kohl stormed into the center of German politics Thursday, waving a
large bundle of money he hopes will buy back favor with the
disgraced political party he brought to the verge of bankruptcy. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   By Imre Karacs, The Independent of London &QL;
