</P>
<P>
   Q: I got my first driver's license and registered to vote as a
new 18-year-old bride in 1960. But I read recently that the voting
age wasn't lowered to 18 until 1972. Can you explain?
</P>
<P>
   A: You must have lived in Georgia, Kentucky or Alaska. Those
