approves the nominations of two controversial Californians, U.S.
District Judge Richard Paez of Los Angeles and civil rights
advocate Marsha Berzon of San Francisco _ to the U.S. 9th Circuit
Court of Appeals in San Francisco. By MARK HELM.
</P>
<P>
