   US-DRUGWAR (Washington) _ Clearing the way for the Clinton
administration's plan to increase military aid to Colombia, a House
committee defeats alternative measures that would have directed
much of the new funding to Colombia's police or to rehabilitation
of US drug addicts. By John Donnelly. 800 words.
