<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-09 22:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2331 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-COLOMBIA-U.S.-490&AMP;ADD     03-09 0646
